column5: Hi everyone, I will be fishing in september on Larder lake. I've been fished there before but have no info about Beaverhouse lake. If somebody been there before and has some info about this lake, tactics, what kind of fish is in there( ...have an ideea what I may find) any areas to try, please pm me . Thank you!
There must be somebody that fished thid bodides of water...right? It' not that far...
